    "faq_GEAWy8": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "accordion_mEJYFa": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How quickly will I see results?",
            "text": "<p>Most people see improvement within the first weeks of using Qure products, but this can vary. </p><p>Some Qure products deliver visible results quickly, like smoother, more hydrated skin after your first Micro-Infusion session. For long-term improvements in wrinkles, acne, or hyperpigmentation, we recommend consistent use for at least 4 to 12 weeks. Like any effective routine, results build over time. </p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_BXXbzd": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often can I use Qure treatments?",
            "text": "<p>It depends on the product. </p><p>Most of our products, including our All-In-One Serum and Q-Rejuvalight Pro LED Mask, are gentle and intended for daily use. Our Micro-Infusion treatments are more intensive and should be used less frequently. We recommend using the Micro Infusion Targeted Eye Patches once per week. and the full Micro-Infusion System once every 2 weeks, for the best results.</p><p>Always follow the usage guidelines for each product and adjust based on how your skin responds.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_Ny8V8k": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I use multiple Qure products together?",
            "text": "<p>Yes, absolutely. Qure products are designed to complement each other as part of a complete routine. </p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_3QAgMR": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "When can I expect to receive my Qure package?",
            "text": "<p>We aim to ship your package as quickly as possible. Processing takes 1-3 business days. You’ll receive an email with tracking info once your package ships.</p><p>Shipping times vary by location but these times are typical per region:</p><ul><li>United States: 8-14 business days</li><li>Canada: 4-6 business days</li><li>UK & Europe: 8-14 business days</li><li>Australia: 8-14 business days</li></ul>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        },
        "accordion_6gWdWg": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where does Qure ship to?",
            "text": "<p>We ship worldwide via FedEx, USPS, or DHL.</p>",
            "link_url": "",
            "link_text": ""
          }
        }
      },
